---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---
<style>
  .icon:hover {
  transform: scale(1.3);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}
</style>
<Card colSpan="md:col-span-2" rowSpan="md:row-span-5" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col mt-1 gap-2">
    <p class="text-center text-sm mb-0">
      Like full-stack developer my primary skillset includes:
    </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-base mb-0">Frontend</p>
    <div class="flex justify-center max-w-full mt-0">
      <Icon title="CSS" name="css3" style="font-size: 28px;" class="icon mx-2 my-1 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="JavaScript" name="js" style="font-size: 32px;" class="icon mx-2 my-0 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="HTML" name="html5" style="font-size: 34px;" class="icon mx-2 my-0 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="Node.js" name="node" style="font-size: 32px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="Git" name="git" style="font-size: 33px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="React" name="react" style="font-size: 41px;" class="icon mx-0 m-0"/>
      <Icon title="Astro" name="astro" style="font-size: 36px;" class="icon mx-0 m-1"/>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-base mb-0">Backend</p>
    <div class="flex justify-center max-w-full mt-0	">
      <Icon title="Python" name="python" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>      
      <Icon title="MySQL" name="mysql" style="font-size: 43px;" class="icon mx-1 my-0 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="SQLite" name="sqlite" style="font-size: 33px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
      <!-- <Icon title="PostgreSQL" name="postgresql" style="font-size: 33px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="Docker" name="docker" style="font-size: 44px;" class="icon mx-1 my-0 m-1"/>
      <Icon title="MongoDB" name="mongodb" style="font-size: 35px;" class="icon mx-0 m-1"/> 
      <Icon title="Pytorch" name="pytorch" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/> 
      <Icon title="TensorFlow" name="tensorflow" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/> -->
      <Icon title="Linux" name="linux" style="font-size: 35px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
    </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm mb-0">
        While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
        job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
        solution for each project.</p>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-base mb-0">Design, Interaction & Arts Tools</p>    
      <div class="flex justify-center max-w-full mt-0 mb-0">
        <Icon title="Photoshop" name="ps" style="font-size: 36px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="After Effects" name="after" style="font-size: 37px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Premiere Pro" name="premier" style="font-size: 31px;" class="icon mx-2 my-2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="TouchDesigner" name="td" style="font-size: 35px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Arduino" name="arduino" style="font-size: 45px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Unity" name="unity" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon -2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Blender" name="blender" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-base mb-0">Data Analysis</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center max-w-full mt-0">
        <Icon title="PowerBI" name="powerbi" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Tableau" name="tableau" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-2 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Excel" name="excel" style="font-size: 37px;" class="icon mx-1 my-0 m-1"/>
        <Icon title="Notion" name="notion" style="font-size: 30px;" class="icon mx-1 m-1"/>
      </div>
    <p class="text-center text-sm mb-0">
      Behind coding, I'm passionate about AI research and 3D experiences.
      An unusual hobby of mine is collecting tiny characters, they're
      interesting pieces of pop culture to me.
    </p>
    </div>
</Card>
